text: Jamshoro District (, ) is a district of Sindh province, Pakistan. Jamshoro is the capital of Jamshoro District. ==Administration== The district is administratively subdivided into the following talukas: * Kotri Tehsil * Manjhand Tehsil * Sehwan Sharif Tehsil * Thana Bulla Khan Tehsil
title: Jamshoro District
